location.fullValue: Trillium IV A Plan, Sugar Mill Plantation

data.description: Like new! Move in ready energy efficient 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in Orleans West. Features include wood floors in living room, 3 cm slab granite countertops in kitchen and bath, ceramic tile flooring in wet areas, beautiful 42" custom cabinets, new carpet, gas fireplace, jetted tub in master bath, recessed can lighting in kitchen, tankless water heater, energy efficient windows, split floorplan, and much more. You are greeted by giant oak tree and lined with beautiful crepe myrtle trees as you drive into the subdivision's entrance. This community is walking distance to Alexander Park with baseball fields, basketball courts and other amenities for outdoor fun. This home did not flood, and flood insurance is not required. Seller is willing to leave the refrigerator, washer, and dryer for new buyer. Schedule your private showing to see this beauty in person!
